ll out what the swab and toothpick couldn\u2019t reach.\n\nFor the case, I like to use a cotton swab for the buildup. Pay extra attention to the charging holes so everything keeps working right. \n\nLast step: 70% isopropyl alcohol on a microfiber towel for a wipe down. These things live in your pocket and your bag all day, so they need the disinfect too.\n\nSave this one for your next cleaning day. \u2728", "hashtags": [], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DaiqlE9iU7c/", "commentsCount": 12, "dimensionsHeight": 1080, "dimensionsWidth": 1080, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-sjc6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/736074232_18442933195140899_2602647568605162400_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_s1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGLd9pqQrKKJ5yE7Pv1q6DgB7MIK3m8x0EkGB_5ssDIwmSxflmMWAdGJrXkSZdV0y8&_nc_ohc=SNZ1Ts8RuDoQ7kNvwHyzZvW&_nc_gid=kUwHLwAeauOCEpswL2kjsw&edm=APU89FABAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQCrUiHV9Z7W49NcqCei9LATIQma4EdYMY5Xqm6jO19X2A&oe=6A61E3FD&_nc_sid=bc0c2c", "images": ["https://scontent-sjc6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/736074232_18442933195140899_2602647568605162400_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_s1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGLd9pqQrKKJ5yE7Pv1q6DgB7MIK3m8x0EkGB_5ssDIwmSxflmMWAdGJrXkSZdV0y8&_nc_ohc=SNZ1Ts8RuDoQ7kNvwHyzZvW&_nc_gid=kUwHLwAeauOCEpswL2kjsw&edm=APU89FABAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQCrUiHV9Z7W49NcqCei9LATIQma4EdYMY5Xqm6jO19X2A&oe=6A61E3FD&_nc_sid=bc0c2c", "https://scontent-sjc6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/736346376_18442933204140899_962178166553751913_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_s1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGLd9pqQrKKJ5yE7Pv1q6DgB7MIK3m8x0EkGB_5ssDIwmSxflmMWAdGJrXkSZdV0y8&_nc_ohc=lJbCvONeBIUQ7kNvwF6XsTo&_nc_gid=kUwHLwAeauOCEpswL2kjsw&edm=APU89FABAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQDQ8gkzDJaMkd0_Ikf6QU1g4c1RyT8_8tlzYrTePqNceA&oe=6A61E20D&_nc_sid=bc0c2c"], "alt": null, "likesCount": 423, "timestamp": "2026-07-08T18:17:11.000Z